{"tid":1825742,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武派核心暴徒","createTime":"2020-01-15T14:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T15:09:36.000Z","uid":204441,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"383a525f86b98e47ca375e1260cc153f28e14817","tid":1825742,"uid":204441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"近排警方破獲多個勇武暴徒武器庫，起出槍械 實彈 炸藥 棍棒。<br />\n啲狗好擅長搜索跟蹤目標嘅，佢哋可能喺示威前線開始跟蹤目標從而破案。<br />\n<br />\n但如果準備武力升級嘅暴徒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔再參與示威前線</span>，最多只係和理非咁行下。咁啲警察就好難鎖定同跟蹤佢哋，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁就大獲啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果準備地下化武裝升級嘅暴徒堅忍潛伏，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係發動攻擊前冇任何行動唔參與示威</span></span>。啲警察冇得鎖定同跟蹤佢，咁政府就<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好難止暴制亂</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望冇人犯法 社會早日平靜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46a5e0a54bf288a4781657d92a5953b594d8ae2","tid":1825742,"uid":112748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"總之要屋企要裝cam save去雲端紀錄！唔怕被人屈"},{"pid":"8f06827ce41e29fb8d8d468c98632a68e3d79a3c","tid":1825742,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d46a5e0a54bf288a4781657d92a5953b594d8ae2","tid":1825742,"uid":112748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"總之要屋企要裝cam save去雲端紀錄！唔怕被人屈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:29:19.000Z","msg":"咁做咪仲伏 仲易俾狗監控"},{"pid":"812d7f3ff8cff2fa3b1392c069bc7e8c5182d2ba","tid":1825742,"uid":204441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d46a5e0a54bf288a4781657d92a5953b594d8ae2","tid":1825742,"uid":112748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:24:29.0